+## Storage Decision
+
+Use a dedicated SQLite database as the durable research memory backend.
+
+Default metadata path:
+
+```text
+~/.summarize/research-memory.sqlite
+```
+
+Default artifact root:
+
+```text
+~/.summarize/research-memory/artifacts/
+```
